title: Low Block Barely There Heels
subtitle: We'll make sure your shoes keep you one stylish step ahead of the crowd
text: Whether you're keeping it simple in sliders, living the high life in heels or joining the fash pack in flatforms, you'll be heading to shoe heaven with our fashion-forward footwear collection. Boots are your day-to-night bestfriend, giving a floral dress that tough twist - add a biker jacket for even more attitude. Find your summer feet in jelly sandals and enjoy balmy nights in block heels. Upper: synthetic suede Lining: synthetic material Outer: synthetic materials.
